<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 12:23:34 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>英国首次针对违反俄罗斯石油限制的船只实施制裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-imposes-first-sanctions-targeting-ships-breaching-russian-oil-restrictions-2024-06-13/</link><description>英国周四对俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京“影子舰队”的船只实施了首次制裁，称这些船只是用来规避西方对俄罗斯石油贸易的制裁的。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 12:07:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-imposes-first-sanctions-targeting-ships-breaching-russian-oil-restrictions-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>克里姆林宫表示与朝鲜建立更密切关系的权利不容置疑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/kremlin-says-its-right-closer-ties-with-north-korea-should-not-be-doubt-2024-06-13/</link><description>克里姆林宫周四表示，俄罗斯与朝鲜发展更密切关系的权利不应受到任何质疑或恐惧，并表示两国关系的潜力非常深厚。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 11:42:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/kremlin-says-its-right-closer-ties-with-north-korea-should-not-be-doubt-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国吉利对欧盟关税决定表示失望，誓言采取“必要措施”维护权利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-geely-expresses-disappointment-eu-tariff-decision-vows-necessary-measures-2024-06-13/</link><description>中国汽车制造商吉利汽车周四对欧盟提高中国制造电动汽车关税的决定表示“非常失望”，并誓言“采取一切必要措施”维护其合法权利。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 11:19:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-geely-expresses-disappointment-eu-tariff-decision-vows-necessary-measures-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>加税后特斯拉预计将提高中国产汽车在欧盟的售价</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-expects-hike-price-china-made-cars-eu-due-tariffs-2024-06-13/</link><description>特斯拉周四在其网站上表示，由于欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车征收进口关税，该公司预计将提高其 Model 3 的价格。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 10:27:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-expects-hike-price-china-made-cars-eu-due-tariffs-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>独家：外交官称，中国在瑞士峰会前推动乌克兰和平计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-pushes-rival-ukraine-peace-plan-before-swiss-summit-diplomats-say-2024-06-13/</link><description>十名外交官表示，中国没有参加周末的乌克兰和平计划峰会，而是一直在游说各国政府制定替代计划，其中一名外交官称北京的行动是对瑞士全球会议的“微妙抵制”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 10:21:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-pushes-rival-ukraine-peace-plan-before-swiss-summit-diplomats-say-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美联储发布后的第二天</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-graphics-2024-06-13/</link><description>达拉·拉纳辛格 (Dhara Ranasinghe) 展望未来一天的市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 10:04:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-graphics-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国企业保留要求欧盟调查猪肉、乳制品的权利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinese-firms-reserve-right-request-investigations-into-eu-pork-dairy-2024-06-13/</link><description>当被问及行业组织是否正在游说其这样做时，中国商务部周四表示，中国企业保留对欧洲乳制品和猪肉进口提出反补贴和反倾销调查的权利。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 09:21:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinese-firms-reserve-right-request-investigations-into-eu-pork-dairy-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲汽车股因对中国关税反应的担忧而下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/european-auto-stocks-fall-further-concerns-over-chinas-tariff-response-2024-06-13/</link><description>欧洲一些最大的汽车制造商周四进一步下跌，原因是担心中国将如何应对欧盟委员会对中国进口电动汽车征收的新关税，以打击他们所说的来自北京的过度补贴。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 09:03:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/european-auto-stocks-fall-further-concerns-over-chinas-tariff-response-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>微软总裁将就安全漏洞向众议院小组作证</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/microsoft-president-testify-before-house-panel-over-security-lapses-2024-06-13/</link><description>微软总裁布拉德·史密斯将于周四在众议院国土安全小组作证，回答有关该公司在过去一年中俄罗斯和中国黑客入侵其系统后的安全实践的问题。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 09:02:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/microsoft-president-testify-before-house-panel-over-security-lapses-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>BRC 首席执行官表示，Shein 在加入英国零售集团时致力于可持续发展和劳工问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shein-committed-engage-sustainability-labour-when-joined-uk-retail-group-brc-ceo-2024-06-13/</link><description>该行业机构负责人告诉路透社，快时尚集团 Shein 在被允许加入英国零售联盟 (BRC) 后，承诺参与可持续发展和道德劳工政策等问题。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 08:03:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shein-committed-engage-sustainability-labour-when-joined-uk-retail-group-brc-ceo-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯演习发射带有假弹头的战术核武器</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-practiced-electronic-missile-launches-during-tactical-nuclear-drills-2024-06-13/</link><description>据俄罗斯精锐核部队称，俄罗斯部署战术核武器进行战斗演习涉及将假核弹头专门运送到前沿储存点和机场，并在那里将其装载到轰炸机上。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 06:03:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-practiced-electronic-missile-launches-during-tactical-nuclear-drills-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲乳制品和猪肉生产商对中国对电动汽车关税的报复保持警惕</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/european-dairy-pork-producers-wary-chinese-retaliation-ev-tariffs-2024-06-13/</link><description>在欧盟周三决定对中国制造的电动汽车征收反补贴税后，从乳制品生产商到猪肉出口商等全球食品公司都对中国可能征收的报复性关税保持高度警惕。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 04:24:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/european-dairy-pork-producers-wary-chinese-retaliation-ev-tariffs-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>从西北到华东，干旱地区面临干旱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/northwest-east-china-parched-baking-regions-face-drought-2024-06-13/</link><description>中国部分地区连续数周降雨稀少，加上酷热，给多个省份带来了干旱，促使当局发出警报并采取行动，尽量减少对农业、水和能源供应的影响。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 03:42:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/northwest-east-china-parched-baking-regions-face-drought-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>多头在创下历史新高后下跌，汽车制造商因关税战而下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-13/</link><description>周四，世界股市从历史高位回落，美国通胀放缓和美联储信号有所缓解的良好因素让位于欧洲新一轮政治和关税引发的疲软。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 03:10:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>洞察：军政府向缅甸叛乱分子学习，建立新的中国无人机舰队</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/learning-myanmars-rebels-junta-builds-new-chinese-drone-fleet-2024-06-13/</link><description>去年，缅甸抵抗战士依靠分散的无人机舰队与东南亚最令人畏惧的军队之一进行战斗，取得了决定性突破。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 02:10:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/learning-myanmars-rebels-junta-builds-new-chinese-drone-fleet-2024-06-13/</guid></item></channel></rss>